WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Hello everyone, I'm Nio.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
I'm going to do something new.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
This summer, Japan, Korea, and the U.S.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:19.000
will come together to meet new friends.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:22.000
We have a special 3-day retreat.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:28.000
A place to meet new friends across nations.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:52.000
The youth from all over Japan, Korea, and the U.S. are gathered here.
They are different from each other,
but as friends who love the same God,
they pray together, chat together, and laugh together.

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:56.000
Small group discussions where you can grow together.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:06.500
Lots of games, activities, and campfires at night —
so many programs to connect across nations.

00:01:06.500 --> 00:01:10.500
And the best location with a view of Mt. Fuji.

00:01:10.500 --> 00:01:20.000
A little distance from everyday life,
in a nature retreat where you encounter God
and meet friends with a shared heart.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:30.000
It's not just a fun camp —
it's a time when new dreams begin to come true.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:38.000
From August 4th to 6th, 2026,
experience something new that God will begin this summer.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:41.000
We are looking forward to your participation!
